schools.name: Krystal School Of Science, Math & Technology

data.description: Built in 2020, this newer Sorrento Built home in the Ranchero Mesa neighborhood is ready for you to call home.   Open floor plan, this 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home offers all the perks of a new build without the wait.  2 Bedrooms are connected to a jack & Jill style bathroom.  Master suite has a barn door entry into the master bathroom with separate tub and shower and large walk in closet.   Large kitchen, plenty of counter space,  walk in pantry and separate laundry room.   3 car garage, large lot with privacy white vinyl fencing and plenty of parking for a RV on a perfect cul-de-sac.   This property is close to Ranchero Road, which makes a commute to the freeway or Apple Valley is a breeze.  .   Might be time to schedule your showing.
